name: Filip W
description: Software engineer with Asperger's. Author, quantum computing nomad, OSS contributor, Microsoft MVP. Works on @omnisharpğŸ¦„ @mapleleafs fan ğŸ’™
tweet: @jbogard The democratization of cloud, data science & embedded systems has lead to a situation where massively complex solutions appear to be easily implemented. But It has put an unfair pressure on lots of engineers, cause it's often expected that everyone can do everything: it's "easy"

name: Filip W
description: Software engineer with Asperger's. Author, quantum computing nomad, OSS contributor, Microsoft MVP. Works on @omnisharpğŸ¦„ @mapleleafs fan ğŸ’™
tweet: @jbogard the "lots of fast changing complex JS Frameworks" is just one manifestation of the "full stack" problem, but to me it goes deeper and it touches the root core of what it means to be a software engineer.

name: Filip W
description: Software engineer with Asperger's. Author, quantum computing nomad, OSS contributor, Microsoft MVP. Works on @omnisharpğŸ¦„ @mapleleafs fan ğŸ’™
tweet:
